lead_paragraph: Golf fans can expect to see havoc, water balls and shots "we don't normally see" at the Masters in Saturday's third round because of strong winds at Augusta National, says former world number one Nick Price.

headline.print_headline: Expect Shots We Don't Normally See at Windy Augusta-Price
